  <summary date="2018-05-15T18:17:12Z" status="Introduced in House">Combat Sexual Harassment in Housing Act

This bill amends the Fair Housing Act to specify that the following&#160;unwelcome conduct in or around a dwelling shall be considered&#160;sufficiently severe or pervasive as to constitute a discriminatory housing practice: (1) unwelcome touching of a sexual nature or groping; or (2) any other unwelcome conduct of a sexual nature that is intended to be coercive, threatening, or intimidating.</summary>
